  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Human Rights Council Interactive Dialogue on Belarus: Joint Statement on Media Freedom in Belarus
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The UK's Permanent Representative in Geneva, Julian Braithwaite, delivered this statement on media freedom in Belarus on behalf of 42 states. </p>

  </div>
</div>

